@layout DefaultLayout
@page "/portfolio/northbrook"

<HeadContent>
    @{
        var openGraphModel = new OpenGraphModel()
        {
            Title = "Northbrook - Fydar",
            Description = "Assign your own unique icon to each of your ScriptableObjects.",
            CanonicalUrl = "https://fydar.dev/portfolio/northbrook",
            Properties = [
                new OpenGraphModelImage()
                {
                    Url = "https://fydar.dev/media/northbrook/social.webp",
                    Alt = "Promotional material for 'Northbrook'."
                }
            ]
        };
        var linkData = new LinkData()
        {
            new LinkDataBreadcrumbList()
            {
                new LinkDataBreadcrumbListItem()
                {
                    Name = "Portfolio",
                    Item = "https://fydar.dev/portfolio/"
                },
                new LinkDataBreadcrumbListItem()
                {
                    Name = "Northbrook",
                    Item = "https://fydar.dev/portfolio/northbrook"
                }
            }
        };
    }
    <OpenGraphComponent Model="@openGraphModel" />
    <LinkDataComponent Model="@linkData" />
</HeadContent>

<section class="fullscreen" data-nosnippet>
    <div class="parallax-frame parallax-focalanchortop" style="--animation-time: 0.5;">

        <picture class="parallax-layer" style="--parallax-multiplier: 0.5">
            <img src="@Assets["media/northbrook/background.webp"]" />
        </picture>

    </div>

    <div class="fullscreen-footer">

        <picture>
            <img class="titlecard" src="@Assets["media/northbrook/titlecard.svg"]" alt="Northbrook College" />
        </picture>

    </div>
</section>

<div class="cascade-container">
    <div class="cascade" style="background: linear-gradient(to right, #cb853f00 0%, #cb853f30 75%, #cb853f14 100%), url('media/noise.svg');">
    </div>
</div>

<HeadingScope>

    <aside>
        <section style="position: sticky; top: 64px;">
            <div style="height: 5rem"></div>
            <TableOfContents />
        </section>

    </aside>

    <section class="container">

        <Heading Level="2" Identifier="course">
            <Text>The Course</Text>
            <Content>

                <p>I joined this course with a strong understanding of game development and programming from my hobbyist experience. This course offered me the freedom to explore programming concepts at my speed. I also had the opportunity to learn the fundamentals of 2D and 3D art.</p>

                <p>I became familiar with 3DS Max which became my tool of choice. This benefited my understanding of 3D graphics greatly. The 3D artistry later inspired my exploration of Substance Designer and other tech art tools.</p>

                <p>Unlike some university courses, I was offered the freedom to make anything I felt like making and the tutors would guide me on how I can meet the marking criteria of the diploma. This was a incredible experience as I gave me the space and freedom I needed to explore games development at my own pace.</p>

                <p>I am personally very interested in RPG games, and so many of the projects I done where themselves RPGs.</p>

                <p>It was during this course where I got my first job working on EITR. It worked out wonderfully as, with permission from the team, I was able to use parts of my work on EITR towards my diploma.</p>

                <CoverGrid>
                    <Cover href="/portfolio/eitr">
                        <Background>
                            <div class="blur" style="background: radial-gradient(130% 66% at 55% 40%, rgb(137 117 120) 0%, rgb(77 62 71) 60%, rgb(49 36 56) 100%)">
                            </div>
                            <img loading="lazy" width="400" height="600" src="@Assets["media/eitr/coverart-background.png"]" alt="Cover art for the game 'EITR'." style="image-rendering: pixelated;" />
                        </Background>
                        <Overlay>
                            <img loading="lazy" class="logo logo-eitr" src="@Assets["media/eitr/titlecard.png"]" alt="Logo for the game 'EITR'." style="image-rendering: pixelated;" />
                        </Overlay>
                    </Cover>
                </CoverGrid>

            </Content>
        </Heading>


        <Heading Level="2" Identifier="extended-diploma">
            <Prefix>2017-2018</Prefix>
            <Text>Extended Diploma in Games Development</Text>
            <SidebarText>Extended Diploma</SidebarText>
            <Content>

                <CardGrid Size="md">
                    <Card href="/portfolio/thedwellers">
                        <FeaturedImage>
                            <picture>
                                <img loading="lazy" width="640" height="480" class="card-image" src="@Assets["media/thedwellers/card.webp"]" alt="Preview of the game 'The Dwellers'" />
                            </picture>
                        </FeaturedImage>
                        <ChildContent>
                            <div class="card-container">
                                <div class="row">
                                    <SvgSprite class="card-keyicon" Link="/icons.svg?v=1#icon-thedwellers" />
                                    <div class="column">
                                        <h3 class="card-header">The Dwellers</h3>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="row">
                                    <p class="card-description">A 3D dungeon crawler game demo with a full RPG item system, featuring a wide range of weapons and other equipment.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </ChildContent>
                    </Card>
                    <Card href="/portfolio/voxelmultiplayer">
                        <FeaturedImage>
                            <picture>
                                <img loading="lazy" width="640" height="480" class="card-image" src="@Assets["media/voxelmultiplayer/card.webp"]" alt="Preview of the Voxel Multiplayer, showing the player character atop of a mountain." />
                            </picture>
                        </FeaturedImage>
                        <ChildContent>
                            <div class="card-container">
                                <div class="row">
                                    <SvgSprite class="card-keyicon" Link="/icons.svg?v=1#icon-voxelmultiplayer" />
                                    <div class="column">
                                        <h3 class="card-header">Voxel Multiplayer</h3>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="row">
                                    <p class="card-description">A voxel-art multiplayer PvP game with a custom voxel-art terrain generator for rendering large worlds.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </ChildContent>
                    </Card>
                </CardGrid>
            </Content>
        </Heading>

        <Heading Level="2" Identifier="summer">
            <Prefix>2017</Prefix>
            <Text>Summer Break</Text>
            <Content>

                <p>It was over the summer break that I joined up with the team from 'Out of the Blue Studios' to work on some collaborative projects.</p>

                <CardGrid Size="md">
                    <Card href="/portfolio/lilypadleap">
                        <FeaturedImage>
                            <picture>
                                <img loading="lazy" width="400" height="300" class="card-image" src="@Assets["media/lilypadleap/card.webp"]" alt="Preview of the game 'Lilypad Leap'." style="image-rendering: pixelated;" />
                            </picture>
                        </FeaturedImage>
                        <ChildContent>
                            <div class="card-container">
                                <div class="row">
                                    <SvgSprite class="card-keyicon" Link="/icons.svg?v=1#icon-lilypadleap" />
                                    <div class="column">
                                        <h3 class="card-header">Lilypad Leap</h3>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="row">
                                    <p class="card-description">The clicker-style where you farm kelp and release fish.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </ChildContent>
                    </Card>
                    <Card href="/portfolio/astralswarm">
                        <FeaturedImage>
                            <picture>
                                <img loading="lazy" width="400" height="300" class="card-image" src="@Assets["media/astralswarm/card.webp"]" alt="Preview of the game 'Astral Swarm'." style="image-rendering: pixelated;" />
                            </picture>
                        </FeaturedImage>
                        <ChildContent>
                            <div class="card-container">
                                <div class="row">
                                    <SvgSprite class="card-keyicon" Link="/icons.svg?v=1#icon-astralswarm" />
                                    <div class="column">
                                        <h3 class="card-header">Astral Swarm</h3>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="row">
                                    <p class="card-description">The clicker-style where you farm kelp and release fish.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </ChildContent>
                    </Card>
                </CardGrid>
            </Content>
        </Heading>

        <Heading Level="2" Identifier="diploma">
            <Prefix>2016-2017</Prefix>
            <Text>Diploma in Games Development</Text>
            <SidebarText>Diploma</SidebarText>
            <Content>
                <CardGrid Size="md">
                    <Card href="/portfolio/thenewearthconflict">
                        <FeaturedImage>
                            <picture>
                                <img loading="lazy" width="640" height="480" class="card-image" src="@Assets["media/thenewearthconflict/card.webp"]" alt="A preview of the game 'The New Earth Conflict' featuring the player ship engaging in combat." />
                            </picture>
                        </FeaturedImage>
                        <ChildContent>
                            <div class="card-container">
                                <div class="row">
                                    <SvgSprite class="card-keyicon" Link="/icons.svg?v=1#icon-thenewearthconflict" />
                                    <div class="column">
                                        <h3 class="card-header">The New Earth Conflict</h3>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="row">
                                    <p class="card-description">A realtime space battle where you take control over a battleship and pilot it into battle against an AI team.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </ChildContent>
                    </Card>
                    <Card href="/portfolio/cryptcrawl">
                        <FeaturedImage>
                            <picture>
                                <img loading="lazy" width="640" height="480" class="card-image" src="@Assets["media/cryptcrawl/keyart-4x3.png"]" alt="A preview of the game 'Crypt Crawl' featuring the protagonist wizard in a brown dungeon." style="image-rendering: pixelated;" />
                            </picture>
                        </FeaturedImage>
                        <ChildContent>
                            <div class="card-container">
                                <div class="row">
                                    <SvgSprite class="card-keyicon" Link="/icons.svg?v=1#icon-cryptcrawl" />
                                    <div class="column">
                                        <h3 class="card-header">Crypt Crawl</h3>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="row">
                                    <p class="card-description">A pixel-art dungeon crawler with a custom tile rendering and rule-based tiles made before Unity created their own.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </ChildContent>
                    </Card>
                </CardGrid>
            </Content>
        </Heading>

    </section>
</HeadingScope>
